`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The GrassInstances pattern is the key reference — outer component tracks `Map<modelPath, capacity>` state (grows-only, prevents GPU re-uploads), inner sub-component calls `useGLTF` unconditionally and updates matrices imperatively in `useFrame` with zero re-renders per frame. For structures/fences/props we need multi-mesh GLB support: traverse scene and create one InstancedMesh per sub-mesh, all sharing the same per-entity transform.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
